NBA ALL-STAR WEEKEND
February 15, 2013
Bradley Beal
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT







Q.   What does it mean to be a part of this?
BRADLEY BEAL:   It's an honor because I'm a rookie.   I'm glad to be here.   It means a lot.   I'm here to have fun and take part in an exciting weekend. 

Q.   Was there a player growing up that you kind of looked up to?
BRADLEY BEAL:   I always liked Allen Iverson.   I loved the way he played.   I did everything like him, everything.   He's the guy I always mimicked. 

